    "Alternative DL approaches have been proposed for de novo design, for instance, molecular graph generation (Li et al., 2018b; Zhou et al., 2019) or fragment-based assembly (Jin et al., 2023c), but they have not been shown to outperform CLMs (Brown et al., 2019; Polykovskiy et al., 2020; Flam-Shepherd et al., 2022).",
